# B-4 cold-process ascent sweep at the perf-reel location. Each 20-frame
# block includes the first draw after the altitude jump; in the play harness
# that makes p95 equal the slowest frame and preserves the hitch signal.
mode fly
weather time 349
teleport 64.120 -46.429 0.05
bench 20
teleport 64.120 -46.429 0.2
bench 20
teleport 64.120 -46.429 0.8
bench 20
teleport 64.120 -46.429 3.0
bench 20
teleport 64.120 -46.429 10.0
bench 20
